mp3", "duration": 500}, {"section": 73, "title": "Chapter 6.  \"So I became a priest: those terms changed all\"", "readers": [6671], "path": "https://www.archive.org/download/ringandbook_1405_librivox/ringandthebook_073_browning_64kb.mp3", "duration": 496}, {"section": 74, "title": "Chapter 6.  \"Sirs, ere the week was out,\"", "readers": [6671], "path": "https://www.archive.org/download/ringandbook_1405_librivox/ringandthebook_074_browning_64kb.mp3", "duration": 507}, {"section": 75, "title": "Chapter 6.  \"I questioned--lifting half the woman's mask\"", "readers": [6671], "path": "https://www.archive.org/download/ringandbook_1405_librivox/ringandthebook_075_browning_64kb.mp3", "duration": 457}, {"section": 76, "title": "Chapter 6.  \"So, I went: crossed street and street: \"The next street's turn,\"", "readers": [6671], "path": "https://www.archive.org/download/ringandbook_1405_librivox/ringandthebook_076_browning_64kb.mp3", "duration": 754}, {"section": 77, "title": "Chapter 6.  \"I answered, \"It shall be when it can be.\"", "readers": [6671], "path": "https://www.archive.org/download/ringandbook_1405_librivox/ringandthebook_077_browning_64kb.mp3", "duration": 389}, {"section": 78, "title": "Chapter 6.  \"I' the grey of dawn it was I found myself\"", "readers": [6671], "path": "https://www.archive.org/download/ringandbook_1405_librivox/ringandthebook_078_browning_64kb.mp3", "duration": 402}, {"section": 79, "title": "Chapter 6.  \"There she stood--leaned there, for the second time,\"", "readers": [6671], "path": "https://www.archive.org/download/ringandbook_1405_librivox/ringandthebook_079_browning_64kb.mp3", "duration": 461}, {"section": 80, "title": "Chapter 6.  \"For the first hour We both were silent in the night, I know\"", "readers": [6671], "path": "https://www.archive.org/download/ringandbook_1405_librivox/ringandthebook_080_browning_64kb.mp3", "duration": 438}, {"section": 81, "title": "Chapter 6.  \"We did go on all night; but at its close\"", "readers": [6671], "path": "https://www.archive.org/download/ringandbook_1405_librivox/ringandthebook_081_browning_64kb.mp3", "duration": 420}, {"section": 82, "title": "Chapter 6.  \"Suddenly I saw The old tower\"", "readers": [6671], "path": "https://www.archive.org/download/ringandbook_1405_librivox/ringandthebook_082_browning_64kb.mp3", "duration": 494}, {"section": 83, "title": "Chapter 6.  \"She started up, stood erect, face to face\"", "readers": [6671], "path": "https://www.archive.org/download/ringandbook_1405_librivox/ringandthebook_083_browning_64kb.mp3", "duration": 461}, {"section": 84, "title": "Chapter 6.  \"When we were parted,--shall I go on there?\"", "readers": [6671], "path": "https://www.archive.org/download/ringandbook_1405_librivox/ringandthebook_084_browning_64kb.mp3", "duration": 469}, {"section": 85, "title": "Chapter 6.  \"And I was just set down to study these\"", "readers": [6671], "path": "https://www.archive.org/download/ringandbook_1405_librivox/ringandthebook_085_browning_64kb.mp3", "duration": 463}, {"section": 86, "title": "Chapter 6.  \"I have done with being judged.\"", "readers": [6671], "path": "https://www.archive.org/download/ringandbook_1405_librivox/ringandthebook_086_browning_64kb.mp3", "duration": 426}, {"section": 87, "title": "Chapter 6.  \"Why, Sirs, what's this? Why, this is sorry and strange!\"", "readers": [6671], "path": "https://www.archive.org/download/ringandbook_1405_librivox/ringandthebook_087_browning_64kb.mp3", "duration": 495}, {"section": 88, "title": "Chapter 6.  \"Sirs, I am quiet again. You see, we are\"", "readers": [6671], "path": "https://www.archive.org/download/ringandbook_1405_librivox/ringandthebook_088_browning_64kb.mp3", "duration": 208}, {"section": 89, "title": "Chapter 7 - Pompilia:  \"I am just seventeen years and five months old\"", "readers": [6671], "path": "https://www.archive.org/download/ringandbook_1405_librivox/ringandthebook_089_browning_64kb.mp3", "duration": 500}, {"section": 90, "title": "Chapter 7.  \"On second thoughts, I hope he will regard\"", "readers": [6671], "path": "https://www.archive.org/download/ringandbook_1405_librivox/ringandthebook_090_browning_64kb.mp3", "duration": 507}, {"section": 91, "title": "Chapter 7.  \"Six days ago when it was New Year's-day\"", "readers": [6671], "path": "https://www.archive.org/download/ringandbook_1405_librivox/ringandthebook_091_browning_64kb.mp3", "duration": 664}, {"section": 92, "title": "Chapter 7.  \"There was a fancy came\"", "readers": [6671], "path": "https://www.archive.org/download/ringandbook_1405_librivox/ringandthebook_092_browning_64kb.mp3", "duration": 471}, {"section": 93, "title": "Chapter 7.  \"When I saw nothing more, the next three weeks\"", "readers": [6671], "path": "https://www.archive.org/download/ringandbook_1405_librivox/ringandthebook_093_browning_64kb.mp3", "duration": 452}, {"section": 94, "title": "Chapter 7.  \"All since is one blank\"", "readers": [6671], "path": "https://www.archive.org/download/ringandbook_1405_librivox/ringandthebook_094_browning_64kb.mp3", "duration": 639}, {"section": 95, "title": "Chapter 7.  \"I felt there was just one thing Guido claimed\"", "readers": [6671], "path": "https://www.archive.org/download/ringandbook_1405_librivox/ringandthebook_095_browning_64kb.mp3", "duration": 559}, {"section": 96, "title": "Chapter 7.  \"So, home I did go; so, the worst befell\"", "readers": [6671], "path": "https://www.archive.org/download/ringandbook_1405_librivox/ringandthebook_096_browning_64kb.mp3", "duration": 460}, {"section": 97, "title": "Chapter 7. \"I had been miserable three drear years\"", "readers": [6671], "path": "https://www.archive.org/download/ringandbook_1405_librivox/ringandthebook_097_browning_64kb.mp3", "duration": 464}, {"section": 98, "title": "Chapter 7.  \"There may have elapsed a week\"", "readers": [6671], "path": "https://www.archive.org/download/ringandbook_1405_librivox/ringandthebook_098_browning_64kb.mp3", "duration": 436}, {"section": 99, "title": "Chapter 7.  \"I returned,\"", "readers": [6671], "path": "https://www.archive.org/download/ringandbook_1405_librivox/ringandthebook_099_browning_64kb.mp3", "duration": 409}, {"section": 100, "title": "Chapter 7.  \"Now, understand here, by no means mistake!\"", "readers": [6671], "path": "https://www.archive.org/download/ringandbook_1405_librivox/ringandthebook_100_browning_64kb.mp3", "duration": 494}, {"section": 101, "title": "Chapter 7.  \"Off she went--\"May he not refuse, that's all\"", "readers": [6671], "path": "https://www.archive.org/download/ringandbook_1405_librivox/ringandthebook_101_browning_64kb.mp3", "duration": 444}, {"section": 102, "title": "Chapter 7.  \"And this man, men call sinner? Jesus Christ!\"", "readers": [6671], "path": "https://www.archive.org/download/ringandbook_1405_librivox/ringandthebook_102_browning_64kb.mp3", "duration": 698}, {"section": 103, "title": "Chapter 7.  \"You see, I will not have the service fail!\"", "readers": [6671], "path": "https://www.archive.org/download/ringandbook_1405_librivox/ringandthebook_103_browning_64kb.mp3", "duration": 575}, {"section": 104, "title": "Chapter 7.  \"Well, and there is more! Yes, my end of breath\"", "readers": [6671], "path": "https://www.archive.org/download/ringandbook_1405_librivox/ringandthebook_104_browning_64kb.mp3", "duration": 371}, {"section": 105, "title": "Chapter 8 - Dominus Hyacinthus de Archangelis Pauperum Procurator:   \"Ah, my Giacinto, he's no ruddy rogue,\"", "readers": [6671], "path": "https://www.archive.org/download/ringandbook_1405_librivox/ringandthebook_105_browning_64kb.mp3", "duration": 567}, {"section": 106, "title": "Chapter 8.  \"Whew!\"", "readers": [6671], "path": "https://www.archive.org/download/ringandbook_1405_librivox/ringandthebook_106_browning_64kb.mp3", "duration": 793}, {"section": 107, "title": "Chapter 8.  \"Yet what do I name \"little and a leak?\"", "readers": [6671], "path": "https://www.archive.org/download/ringandbook_1405_librivox/ringandthebook_107_browning_64kb.mp3", "duration": 605}, {"section": 108, "title": "Chapter 8.  \"So, doubtless, had I needed argue here\"", "readers": [6671], "path": "https://www.archive.org/download/ringandbook_1405_librivox/ringandthebook_108_browning_64kb.mp3", "duration": 718}, {"section": 109, "title": "Chapter 8.  \"May Gigia have remembered, nothing stings\"", "readers": [6671], "path": "https://www.archive.org/download/ringandbook_1405_librivox/ringandthebook_109_browning_64kb.mp3", "duration": 693}, {"section": 110, "title": "Chapter 8.  \"Have I proved\"", "readers": [6671], "path": "https://www.archive.org/download/ringandbook_1405_librivox/ringandthebook_110_browning_64kb.mp3", "duration": 817}, {"section": 111, "title": "Chapter 8.  \"Pause and breathe!\"", "readers": [6671], "path": "https://www.archive.org/download/ringandbook_1405_librivox/ringandthebook_111_browning_64kb.mp3", "duration": 612}, {"section": 112, "title": "Chapter 8. \"And now, sea widens and the coast is clear.\"", "readers": [6671], "path": "https://www.archive.org/download/ringandbook_1405_librivox/ringandthebook_112_browning_64kb.mp3", "duration": 559}, {"section": 113, "title": "Chapter 8.  \"Here fall to be considered those same six\"", "readers": [6671], "path": "https://www.archive.org/download/ringandbook_1405_librivox/ringandthebook_113_browning_64kb.mp3", "duration": 566}, {"section": 114, "title": "Chapter 8.  \"Third aggravation: that our act was done--\"", "readers": [6671], "path": "https://www.archive.org/download/ringandbook_1405_librivox/ringandthebook_114_browning_64kb.mp3", "duration": 512}, {"section": 115, "title": "Chapter 8.  \"But wait awhile!\"", "readers": [6671], "path": "https://www.archive.org/download/ringandbook_1405_librivox/ringandthebook_115_browning_64kb.mp3", "duration": 648}, {"section": 116, "title": "Chapter 8.  \"Talking of which flea\"", "readers": [6671], "path": "https://www.archive.org/download/ringandbook_1405_librivox/ringandthebook_116_browning_64kb.mp3", "duration": 515}, {"section": 117, "title": "Chapter 8.  \"And now, thou excellent the Governor!\"", "readers": [6671], "path": "https://www.archive.org/download/ringandbook_1405_librivox/ringandthebook_117_browning_64kb.mp3", "duration": 784}, {"section": 118, "title": "Chapter 9 -  Juris Doctor Johannes-Baptista Bottinius:  \"Had I God's leave, how I would alter things!\"", "readers": [6671], "path": "https://www.archive.org/download/ringandbook_1405_librivox/ringandthebook_118_browning_64kb.mp3", "duration": 508}, {"section": 119, "title": "Chapter 9.  \"End we exordium, Phaebus plucks my ear!\"", "readers": [6671], "path": "https://www.archive.org/download/ringandbook_1405_librivox/ringandthebook_119_browning_64kb.mp3", "duration": 575}, {"section": 120, "title": "Chapter 9.  \"For lo, advancing Hymen and his pomp!\"", "readers": [6671], "path": "https://www.archive.org/download/ringandbook_1405_librivox/ringandthebook_120_browning_64kb.mp3", "duration": 728}, {"section": 121, "title": "Chapter 9.  \"Enough! Prepare,\"", "readers": [6671], "path": "https://www.archive.org/download/ringandbook_1405_librivox/ringandthebook_121_browning_64kb.mp3", "duration": 473}, {"section": 122, "title": "Chapter 9.  \"From all which, I deduce--the lady here\"", "readers": [6671], "path": "https://www.archive.org/download/ringandbook_1405_librivox/ringandthebook_122_browning_64kb.mp3", "duration": 569}, {"section": 123, "title": "Chapter 9.  \"Thus Would I defend the step,--were the thing true\"", "readers": [6671], "path": "https://www.archive.org/download/ringandbook_1405_librivox/ringandthebook_123_browning_64kb.mp3", "duration": 546}, {"section": 124, "title": "Chapter 9.  \"Fit place, methinks,\"", "readers": [6671], "path": "https://www.archive.org/download/ringandbook_1405_librivox/ringandthebook_124_browning_64kb.mp3", "duration": 656}, {"section": 125, "title": "Chapter 9.  \"And so he was contented--one must do\"", "readers": [6671], "path": "https://www.archive.org/download/ringandbook_1405_librivox/ringandthebook_125_browning_64kb.mp3", "duration": 481}, {"section": 126, "title": "Chapter 9.  \"It happened once,--begins this foolish Jew,\"", "readers": [6671], "path": "https://www.archive.org/download/ringandbook_1405_librivox/ringandthebook_126_browning_64kb.mp3", "duration": 580}, {"section": 127, "title": "Chapter 9.  \"Forgive me this digression--that I stand\"", "readers": [6671], "path": "https://www.archive.org/download/ringandbook_1405_librivox/ringandthebook_127_browning_64kb.mp3", "duration": 651}, {"section": 128, "title": "Chapter 9.  \"Yet doubt he dares!\"", "readers": [6671], "path": "https://www.archive.org/download/ringandbook_1405_librivox/ringandthebook_128_browning_64kb.mp3", "duration": 520}, {"section": 129, "title": "Chapter 9.  \"Your \"this,\" friend, is extraneous to the law,\"", "readers": [6671], "path": "https://www.archive.org/download/ringandbook_1405_librivox/ringandthebook_129_browning_64kb.mp3", "duration": 591}, {"section": 130, "title": "Chapter 10 - The Pope:  \"Like to Ahasuerus, that shrewd prince,\"", "readers": [6671], "path": "https://www.archive.org/download/ringandbook_1405_librivox/ringandthebook_130_browning_64kb.mp3", "duration": 679}, {"section": 131, "title": "Chapter 10.  \"But, after John, came Sergius, reaffirmed\"", "readers": [6671], "path": "https://www.archive.org/download/ringandbook_1405_librivox/ringandthebook_131_browning_64kb.mp3", "duration": 730}, {"section": 132, "title": "Chapter 10.  \"O pale departure, dim disgrace of day!\"", "readers": [6671], "path": "https://www.archive.org/download/ringandbook_1405_librivox/ringandthebook_132_browning_64kb.mp3", "duration": 624}, {"section": 133, "title": "Chapter 10.  \"This is why Guido is found reprobate.\"", "readers": [6671], "path": "https://www.archive.org/download/ringandbook_1405_librivox/ringandthebook_133_browning_64kb.mp3", "duration": 634}, {"section": 134, "title": "Chapter 10.  \"He purposes this marriage, I remark,\"", "readers": [6671], "path": "https://www.archive.org/download/ringandbook_1405_librivox/ringandthebook_134_browning_64kb.mp3", "duration": 628}, {"section": 135, "title": "Chapter 10.  \"Whereby the man so far attains his end\"", "readers": [6671], "path": "https://www.archive.org/download/ringandbook_1405_librivox/ringandthebook_135_browning_64kb.mp3", "duration": 658}, {"section": 136, "title": "Chapter 10.  \"So is the murder managed, sin conceived\"", "readers": [6671], "path": "https://www.archive.org/download/ringandbook_1405_librivox/ringandthebook_136_browning_64kb.mp3", "duration": 805}, {"section": 137, "title": "Chapter 10.  \"Nay, more i' the background, yet? Unnoticed forms\"", "readers": [6671], "path": "https://www.archive.org/download/ringandbook_1405_librivox/ringandthebook_137_browning_64kb.mp3", "duration": 565}, {"section": 138, "title": "Chapter 10.  \"And surely not so very much apart\"", "readers": [6671], "path": "https://www.archive.org/download/ringandbook_1405_librivox/ringandthebook_138_browning_64kb.mp3", "duration": 640}, {"section": 139, "title": "Chapter 10.  \"So do I see, pronounce on all and some\"", "readers": [6671], "path": "https://www.archive.org/download/ringandbook_1405_librivox/ringandthebook_139_browning_64kb.mp3", "duration": 374}, {"section": 140, "title": "Chapter 10.  \"O Thou,--as represented here to me\"", "readers": [6671], "path": "https://www.archive.org/download/ringandbook_1405_librivox/ringandthebook_140_browning_64kb.mp3", "duration": 542}, {"section": 141, "title": "Chapter 10.  \"Neither does this astonish at the end,\"", "readers": [6671], "path": "https://www.archive.org/download/ringandbook_1405_librivox/ringandthebook_141_browning_64kb.mp3", "duration": 863}, {"section": 142, "title": "Chapter 10.  \"And is this little all that was to be?\"", "readers": [6671], "path": "https://www.archive.org/download/ringandbook_1405_librivox/ringandthebook_142_browning_64kb.mp3", "duration": 751}, {"section": 143, "title": "Chapter 10.  \"How should I answer this Euripides?\"", "readers": [6671], "path": "https://www.archive.org/download/ringandbook_1405_librivox/ringandthebook_143_browning_64kb.mp3", "duration": 770}, {"section": 144, "title": "Chapter 10.  \"Still, I stand here, not off the stage though close\"", "readers": [6671], "path": "https://www.archive.org/download/ringandbook_1405_librivox/ringandthebook_144_browning_64kb.mp3", "duration": 825}, {"section": 145, "title": "Chapter 11 - Guido:  \"You are the Cardinal Acciaiuoli, and you,\"", "readers": [6671], "path": "https://www.archive.org/download/ringandbook_1405_librivox/ringandthebook_145_browning_64kb.mp3", "duration": 637}, {"section": 146, "title": "Chapter 11.  \"Life!\"", "readers": [6671], "path": "https://www.archive.org/download/ringandbook_1405_librivox/ringandthebook_146_browning_64kb.mp3", "duration": 786}, {"section": 147, "title": "Chapter 11.  \"That's Nature's way of loosing cord!--but Art,\"", "readers": [6671], "path": "https://www.archive.org/download/ringandbook_1405_librivox/ringandthebook_147_browning_64kb.mp3", "duration": 944}, {"section": 148, "title": "Chapter 11.  \"I say that, long ago, when things began,\"", "readers": [6671], "path": "https://www.archive.org/download/ringandbook_1405_librivox/ringandthebook_148_browning_64kb.mp3", "duration": 563}, {"section": 149, "title": "Chapter 11.  \"And the Pope breaks talk with ambassador,\"", "readers": [6671], "path": "https://www.archive.org/download/ringandbook_1405_librivox/ringandthebook_149_browning_64kb.mp3", "duration": 562}, {"section": 150, "title": "Chapter 11.  \"Enough of the hypocrites. But you, Sirs, you--\"", "readers": [6671], "path": "https://www.archive.org/download/ringandbook_1405_librivox/ringandthebook_150_browning_64kb.mp3", "duration": 648}, {"section": 151, "title": "Chapter 11.  \"Yes, presently...what hour is fleeting now?\"", "readers": [6671], "path": "https://www.archive.org/download/ringandbook_1405_librivox/ringandthebook_151_browning_64kb.mp3", "duration": 832}, {"section": 152, "title": "Chapter 11.  \"Why must your nephews begin breathing spice\"", "readers": [6671], "path": "https://www.archive.org/download/ringandbook_1405_librivox/ringandthebook_152_browning_64kb.mp3", "duration": 628}, {"section": 153, "title": "Chapter 11.  \"Panciatichi!\"", "readers": [6671], "path": "https://www.archive.org/download/ringandbook_1405_librivox/ringandthebook_153_browning_64kb.mp3", "duration": 613}, {"section": 154, "title": "Chapter 11.  \"All which just means,\"", "readers": [6671], "path": "https://www.archive.org/download/ringandbook_1405_librivox/ringandthebook_154_browning_64kb.mp3", "duration": 594}, {"section": 155, "title": "Chapter 11.  \"'Tis I preach while the hour-glass runs and runs!\"", "readers": [6671], "path": "https://www.archive.org/download/ringandbook_1405_librivox/ringandthebook_155_browning_64kb.mp3", "duration": 541}, {"section": 156, "title": "Chapter 11.  \"Just this immaculate official stares,\"", "readers": [6671], "path": "https://www.archive.org/download/ringandbook_1405_librivox/ringandthebook_156_browning_64kb.mp3", "duration": 523}, {"section": 157, "title": "Chapter 11.  \"And then my Trial,--'tis my Trial that bites\"", "readers": [6671], "path": "https://www.archive.org/download/ringandbook_1405_librivox/ringandthebook_157_browning_64kb.mp3", "duration": 690}, {"section": 158, "title": "Chapter 11.  \"Thus The time's arrived when, ancient Roman-like,\"", "readers": [6671], "path": "https://www.archive.org/download/ringandbook_1405_librivox/ringandthebook_158_browning_64kb.mp3", "duration": 596}, {"section": 159, "title": "Chapter 11.  \"So, let death atone!\"", "readers": [6671], "path": "https://www.archive.org/download/ringandbook_1405_librivox/ringandthebook_159_browning_64kb.mp3", "duration": 793}, {"section": 160, "title": "Chapter 11.  \"You too are petrifactions of a kind:\"", "readers": [6671], "path": "https://www.archive.org/download/ringandbook_1405_librivox/ringandthebook_160_browning_64kb.mp3", "duration": 905}, {"section": 161, "title": "Chapter 12 - The Book and the Ring:  \"Here were the end, had anything an end:\"", "readers": [6671], "path": "https://www.archive.org/download/ringandbook_1405_librivox/ringandthebook_161_browning_64kb.mp3", "duration": 454}, {"section": 162, "title": "Chapter 12.  \"Now for the thing; no sooner the decree\"", "readers": [6671], "path": "https://www.archive.org/download/ringandbook_1405_librivox/ringandthebook_162_browning_64kb.mp3", "duration": 654}, {"section": 163, "title": "Chapter 12.  \"And so forth,--follow name and place and date:\"", "readers": [6671], "path": "https://www.archive.org/download/ringandbook_1405_librivox/ringandthebook_163_browning_64kb.mp3", "duration": 629}, {"section": 164, "title": "Chapter 12.  \"I looked that Rome should have the natural gird\"", "readers": [6671], "path": "https://www.archive.org/download/ringandbook_1405_librivox/ringandthebook_164_browning_64kb.mp3", "duration": 713}, {"section": 165, "title": "Chapter 12.  \"For me, the weary and the worn, who prompt\"", "readers": [6671], "path": "https://www.archive.org/download/ringandbook_1405_librivox/ringandthebook_165_browning_64kb.mp3", "duration": 605}, {"section": 166, "title": "Chapter 12.  \"Alack, Bottini, what is my next word\"", "readers": [6671], "path": "https://www.archive.org/download/ringandbook_1405_librivox/ringandthebook_166_browning_64kb.mp3", "duration": 522}]}